   {:e #blake3 "0278352d31a9ce4a5bf5da1d8eaa547749b700ac25ce864ef1a9b4189817646b" :a :spec/source-file :v "02-schema.md" :op :assert}
   {:e #blake3 "0278352d31a9ce4a5bf5da1d8eaa547749b700ac25ce864ef1a9b4189817646b" :a :element/body :v "**Traces to**: ADRS SR-009\n**Verification**: `V:PROP`\n**Stage**: 0–4 (progressive)\n\n#### Level 0 (Algebraic Law)\n```\nSchema is organized into 6 layers:\n  Layer 0: Meta-schema (18 axiomatic attributes)        — Stage 0\n  Layer 1: Agent & Provenance (2 types, 16 attributes)  — Stage 0\n  Layer 2: DDIS Core (12 types, 72 attributes)          — Stage 0–1\n  Layer 3: Discovery & Exploration (5 types, 28 attrs)  — Stage 1–2\n  Layer 4: Coordination (7 types, 35 attributes)        — Stage 2–3\n  Layer 5: Workflow & Task (5 types, 27 attributes)     — Stage 3–4\n\nEach layer depends only on layers below it.\n```\n\n#### Level 1 (State Invariant)\nAttributes in Layer N reference only entity types defined in Layers 0..N.\n\n**Falsification**: A Layer 1 attribute that references a Layer 3 entity type.\n\n---" :op :assert}
   {:e #blake3 "0278352d31a9ce4a5bf5da1d8eaa547749b700ac25ce864ef1a9b4189817646b" :a :spec/statement :v "``` Schema is organized into 6 layers: Layer 0: Meta-schema (18 axiomatic attributes)        — Stage 0 Layer 1: Agent & Provenance (2 types, 16 attributes)  — Stage 0 Layer 2: DDIS Core (12 types, 72 attributes)          — Stage 0–1 Layer 3: Discovery & Exploration (5 types, 28 attrs)  — Stage 1–2 Layer 4: Coordination (7 types, 35 attributes)        — Stage 2–3 Layer 5: Workflow & Task (5 types, 27 attributes)     — Stage 3–4 Each layer depends only on layers below it. ```" :op :assert}
   {:e #blake3 "0278352d31a9ce4a5bf5da1d8eaa547749b700ac25ce864ef1a9b4189817646b" :a :spec/falsification :v "A Layer 1 attribute that references a Layer 3 entity type." :op :assert}
