   {:e #blake3 "a4a569aaa5628488336a20d52fd6349488d6ada749974215c8e95e3cec098134" :a :element/body :v "**Traces to**: ADRS AS-008\n**Verification**: `V:PROP`\n**Stage**: 2\n\n#### Level 0 (Algebraic Law)\n```\n∀ projection patterns P with access_count(P) > reification_threshold (default 3):\n  P is stored as a first-class entity with significance score\n  P is discoverable via ASSOCIATE\n```\n\n#### Level 1 (State Invariant)\nUseful query patterns are promoted to entities, enabling the system to learn\n\"good ways to look at data.\"\n\n**Falsification**: A projection pattern accessed 10+ times that is not stored as an entity.\n\n---" :op :assert}
   {:e #blake3 "a4a569aaa5628488336a20d52fd6349488d6ada749974215c8e95e3cec098134" :a :spec/statement :v "``` ∀ projection patterns P with access_count(P) > reification_threshold (default 3): P is stored as a first-class entity with significance score P is discoverable via ASSOCIATE ```" :op :assert}
   {:e #blake3 "a4a569aaa5628488336a20d52fd6349488d6ada749974215c8e95e3cec098134" :a :spec/falsification :v "A projection pattern accessed 10+ times that is not stored as an entity." :op :assert}
